<Route path="post">   

            <Route index element={
              <NewPost

                  postTitle={postTitle}

                />} />

            <Route path=":id" element={

                  posts={posts}
                  handleDelete={handleDelete}
                  deletedposts = {deletedposts}
                />} />

        </Route>
